  "prompt": "Which is the best CAT coaching centre in Ghaziabad?",
  "response": "The best CAT coaching center in Ghaziabad can vary based on individual preferences, teaching quality, faculty, study materials, and success rates. Some of the most popular and reputable CAT coaching centers in Ghaziabad include:\n\n1. **TIME (Triumphant Institute of Management Education)**  \n   - Known for its structured curriculum, experienced faculty, and comprehensive study material.  \n   - Offers both classroom and online programs.  \n\n2. **IMS (Institute of Management Studies)**  \n   - Well-established for CAT preparation with a focus on conceptual clarity and test-taking strategies.  \n   - Provides personalized attention and mock tests.  \n\n3. **Career Launcher**  \n   - Offers extensive study material, regular mock tests, and experienced faculty.  \n   - Known for its strong track record in CAT results.  \n\n4. **BYJU'S (formerly Think & Learn)**  \n   - Provides online courses with flexibility and personalized learning plans.  \n   - Known for its interactive video lectures and test series.  \n\n5. **Jamboree Education**  \n   - Specializes in test preparation with a focus on quantitative and verbal sections.  \n   - Offers both classroom and online programs.  \n\n6. **Geo CAT Classes**  \n   - A local institute with a good reputation for CAT coaching in Ghaziabad.  \n   - Known for its affordable fees and personalized attention.  \n\nBefore choosing a coaching center, consider visiting the institutes, attending demo classes, and checking reviews from past students. Factors like location, fee structure, batch size, and your learning style should also guide your decision.",
